title: 583. MVP, Defensive Player of the Year, Rookie of the Year & Coach of the Year Predictions
itunes:title: 583. MVP, Defensive Player of the Year, Rookie of the Year & Coach of the Year Predictions
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys discuss the BYU vs. Navy game and the importance of physical practices (:48). Next, the pair react to the news of Texans QB Deshaun Watson's contract extension (8:13) and Chargers WR Keenan Allen's contract extension (17:11). Then, the duo analyze the Titans signing edge rusher Jadeveon Clowney (20:51). After that, the guys preview the Texans vs. Chiefs kickoff game by looking at the Texans' roster and Chiefs' defense (29:51). Next, DJ and Bucky each give their MVP, Defensive Player of the Year, Rookie of the Year and Coach of the Year predictions (37:53). To wrap up the show, the guys discuss the Eagles signing QB Josh McCown to their practice squad, while allowing him to live in Texas (42:53).
